des:
Programmer Quotes provides nice and wisdom Quotes from Programmers around the world.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Programmer Quotes" or "Alexa, open Programmer Quotes" to get a Quote from a Programmer.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
